\end_inset

 and the public value 
\begin_inset Formula $\pub_{i}$
\end_inset

.
 The denominator is the variance of the private benefit of development,
 conditional on the signal 
\begin_inset Formula $\se_{i}$
\end_inset

.
 The first term on the right hand side is the expected benefit of conserving
 the parcel.
 This expression can thus be rewritten
